  "display_name": "Infrastructure Resilience and Vulnerability Analysis",
  "description": "This cluster of papers focuses on the assessment and enhancement of infrastructure resilience, particularly in the context of interdependent systems and disaster management. It explores quantitative analysis, network interdependencies, and vulnerability assessment of critical infrastructure, with a specific emphasis on seismic resilience and transportation networks.",
